Detailed Description

The TRE Handler Interface.

This interface should be fulfilled by any plug-in that wants to handle a TRE. View the documentation above for each of the methods below. In addition to the methods, there is an optional data field (of type NITF_DATA*) which allows the plug-in to store data associated with the Handler.
